SRE & Devopos 

DevOps engineers focus on automating infrastructure and building CI/CD pipelines to deliver features faster and more reliably.


SRE:
“SRE engineers focus on system reliability, security, monitoring, incident management, and enforcing SLOs and SLAs to maintain production stability and performance.”

______________________________
tasks:
“Daily, I review monitoring dashboards and alerts,
resolve production incident tickets, perform root cause analysis, Optimize auto-scaling and resource usage,
support deployments, and continuously improve reliability through automating repetitive tasks .”

